snippet.title: BUCKETZ Official Game Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
BUCKETZ
A Game about Balance... and pretty much everything else.

Join the Nine, the most unlikely gang of heroes in their desperate quest to restore balance to all things and uncover the mystery behind the Dark Bucket and its minions.

Coming Soon To iPhone, iPod Touch and iPad

visit www.picnichippo.com for more info
